## 10. Phase 1 requirements: screen sharing

### Objective

Allow the agent to share the entire screen in Google Meet.

### Requirements

#### FR-1.1: Start screen share

The agent should be able to start sharing the entire Mac screen.

#### FR-1.2: Visible work

When performing tasks, the agent should make its actions visible to the meeting participants.

#### FR-1.3: Clean desktop

The dedicated Mac should have a clean desktop and no personal files visible.

### MVP note

Screen sharing is useful for the hackathon demo, but it should come after the voice loop works. The first emotional “wow” moment is hearing the agent participate in the call.

