## 17. Mac worker design

### Worker responsibilities

The Mac worker should:

1. Start on the dedicated Mac.
2. Connect to hosted backend using WebSocket.
3. Wait for commands.
4. Open Chrome with the agent profile.
5. Join Google Meet.
6. Set correct audio devices.
7. Start Gemini Live session.
8. Route meeting audio to Gemini.
9. Route Gemini spoken output back into Meet.
10. Send status updates to backend.

### Worker internal modules

```text
worker/
  main.py
  websocket_client.py
  meet_controller.py
  audio_router.py
  gemini_live_client.py
  turn_taking.py
  browser_controller.py
  status.py
```

### Suggested worker states

```text
IDLE
CONNECTING_TO_BACKEND
READY
JOINING_MEETING
IN_WAITING_ROOM
IN_MEETING
LISTENING
THINKING
SPEAKING
ERROR
```

