## 20. Success metrics

### Phase 0 success metrics

The first milestone is successful if:

1. User can paste a Meet link into the web app.
2. Mac worker receives the command.
3. Chrome opens the meeting link.
4. Agent joins the meeting.
5. Agent hears people speaking.
6. Agent responds out loud.
7. Agent does not constantly interrupt.
8. Agent can answer at least five basic spoken questions during the meeting.

### Example test questions

```text
Can you hear me?
What is your role in this meeting?
Can you summarize what I just said?
Can you wait until I finish speaking before responding?
Can you explain what you can do next?
```

### Phase 4 success metrics

The full hackathon demo is successful if:

1. Agent joins the meeting.
2. Agent speaks naturally.
3. Agent shares its screen.
4. Agent opens project brief.
5. Agent summarizes brief.
6. Agent browses a website.
7. Agent creates Trello cards.
8. Agent opens Trello board showing created cards.

