## 22. Implementation roadmap

### Milestone 1: Worker connection

Build:

* Hosted backend
* WebSocket worker connection
* Web app status page

Done when:

```text
Mac worker appears as “online” in web app.
```

### Milestone 2: Join Google Meet

Build:

* Web app input for Meet link
* Backend command
* Mac worker opens Chrome
* Worker joins Meet

Done when:

```text
Agent account appears inside the Google Meet call.
```

### Milestone 3: Audio capture

Build:

* Virtual audio route
* Capture Meet audio
* Send test audio to local logger or simple STT/debug output

Done when:

```text
Worker can detect that someone in the meeting is speaking.
```

### Milestone 4: Audio output

Build:

* Route generated/test audio into Google Meet microphone

Done when:

```text
People in the meeting can hear the agent say a test phrase.
```

### Milestone 5: Gemini Live conversation

Build:

* Stream meeting audio to Gemini Live
* Receive spoken response
* Route response to Meet
* Add silence-based response gating

Done when:

```text
People can ask the agent simple questions and hear answers in the meeting.
```

### Milestone 6: Screen sharing

Build:

* Start full-screen sharing
* Make agent actions visible

Done when:

```text
Participants can see the agent’s screen.
```

### Milestone 7: File reading

Build:

* Workspace folder reader
* PDF/DOCX/TXT/Markdown/spreadsheet/image extraction
* `read_workspace_file` tool

Done when:

```text
Agent can summarize a project brief from the workspace folder.
```

### Milestone 8: Website browsing

Build:

* Open website tool
* Page extraction/summarization
* Browser visible on shared screen

Done when:

```text
Agent can browse a website and summarize what it found.
```

### Milestone 9: Trello cards

Build:

* Trello API integration
* Create cards
* Open board after creation

Done when:

```text
Agent creates Trello cards from the brief and meeting discussion.
```

