## 23. Recommended first build

Start with this exact first target:

```text
From the web app, paste a Google Meet link.
The dedicated Mac joins the Meet.
Someone says: “Can you hear me?”
The agent waits for silence and says out loud: “Yes, I can hear you.”
```

This is the real foundation.

After that, add:

```text
“Can you summarize what I just said?”
```

Then:

```text
“Can you explain what you can do in this meeting?”
```

Only after those work, add file reading and Trello.

